Day 84 – Road to Fluent Spanish Summary
Today’s study session focused on reinforcing and retaining material from Pimsleur Unit 3 Lesson 5 while continuing daily practice through Duolingo, Memrise, and this week’s conversational phrase set. Lesson 5 required a second day of review due to the amount of new vocabulary and sentence structure introduced, and today’s review significantly improved recall.

Completed Today
