Overall Progress
Recall continues to improve noticeably across both new and previously learned material. Most restaurant, travel, work, and small-talk phrases can now be recalled with little hesitation. Older Pimsleur lessons are holding up well, indicating that the spaced repetition and daily review process is working. Lesson 5 was challenging, but by the end of today’s review the vast majority of the material could be recalled without assistance.

Tomorrow the plan is to begin the next Pimsleur lesson while continuing to reinforce previous conversational phrases through mixed review and real-world style practice.
